title: Make Grand more Grander
body:
Make the Grand more Grander.

Take a look and evaluate the tokenomics of the Olympus project (OHM). 

They have a very smart and productive tokenomics based on precise fixed income bonding.

This is the future of the DeFi.  We need to go in this direction in my opinion

Imagine what the Grand could be if we followed the path of accurate fixed income without inflation.
choices: Yes, we need the same approach
No, this is a road to nowhere
